// Two modes of hardening:
//
//   mineralize(engine, "react", 0)
//     → react/0 is immutable.  Everything else stays dynamic.
//     → Additive, one-way.  Call multiple times for multiple preds.
//
//   fossilize(engine)
//     → ALL clauses frozen.  Only ephemeral survives.
